{"type": "article", "id": 60172, "title": "这款环保运动鞋，是用干草和回收塑料瓶制作的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-10T22:48:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 55824, "name": "COLEEN"}, {"id": 55825, "name": "STUDIO PESI"}, {"id": 55826, "name": "nat-2"}, {"id": 55827, "name": "Nicole McLaughlin"}, {"id": 55828, "name": "Sarah Wertzberger"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 104, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190110200735D3TqIRpv7nUP1NeL.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #939090; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #939090} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>100% Vegan Sneakers by nat-2</h3><p>德国高端运动鞋品牌 nat-2 最近推出了一款用真正的干草制作的纯植物运动鞋。它看上去与普通的环保产品并无差别。作为一款 100% 纯植物产品，这双中性款运动鞋的鞋帮采用真正的可持续回收干草与干花材料制作，根据鞋款式不同，材料覆盖了鞋面多达 50%的面积。</p><p>经过压缩的干草材料被使用在基底层，有着天然的山地气味。每双灵感源自阿尔卑斯的运动鞋都独一无二，鞋面还会随时间发生变化，最终获得独一无二的色泽与外观。这种已获得专利的材料在德国与奥地利两地开发，最终运动鞋则在意大利手工制作。</p><p>所有鞋履全部为 100%植物材质，配备软垫和抗菌软木内底。其中鞋面上看上去像小山羊皮或软皮的材质实际上采用回收塑料瓶制造。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901102008156jrvfkcIDHZJb2AO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200816qz4bIF3HLtQhkTlm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200818hHbM2KNsjm4xrT5B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200826kR6jc7QgUhrbxDO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200826ORZJAmrcSkHEKoMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/nat-2-100-vegan-sneakers-hay-plastic-bottles-01-09-2019/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Original Modern Blanket Designs by Sarah Wertzberger</h3><p>跨学科艺术家 Sarah Wertzberger  一直关注油漆、粘土以及纺织工艺。最近，她通过手工工艺、工业化生产流程以及数字编织的结合方式，设计并制作了一系列原始美感的毯子。</p><p>Sarah Wertzberger 持续研究材料和工艺，探索了艺术、设计、工艺、技术中的各种色彩游戏。她倚赖自己的直觉以及不同材料之间的限制来引导最终的设计结果，最终呈现出一个现代感十足的俏皮系列，又强化了传统的制作方法。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200905IYgwWcDPBiEObQsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200905ItrUqbc3zAjLOspC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200906lqiZGWumLE02P53y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110200906xSiZ9OuDMgqln1fh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901102009060B4cGT35tVkKHMym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901102009070clhsfdVFaJC36ji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901102009112OJhUYc1KgIpMkHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.sarahwertzberger.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sarah Wertzberger</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mist by STUDIO PESI</h3><p>那种挂在门口的串珠窗帘，只要有人通过，就会混在一起叮当作响。最近，韩国设计工作室 STUDIO PESI 为其重新设计了现代版本，意在传达出雾状的感觉，因此被命名为 Mist。</p><p>网格并没有明确的边界，好似被迷雾吞没了一半，无法分辨出来。</p><p>这种热塑性聚氨酯模块提供三种尺寸，可连接的模块允许各种配置的幕帘。它可以作为门帘使用，也可以成为房间隔断，或是加入柜体中成为门挡，或许能帮助家居空间添入一些梦幻迷雾般的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201101GnpvbuzQNjIKU28T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019011020110107EgkvdCRIUW1jLw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201102OYISZCDufcRwnjel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201102UrkKfGyaAMmIeCL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201103u0PlxB78kjdKAR4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201103W3s85QKNgB2FJhz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201103psRjN7HmzCGY3Unl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.studiopesi.com/mist\" rel=\"nofollow\">STUDIO PESI</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Coleen Electric Bicycle</h3><p>为了探索城市旅行的乐趣，在最近的 CES 2019 展会上，COLEEN 推出一款电动自行车，其大胆、优雅而复古的设计，灵感来源于法国设计师  Jean Prouvé 的作品，延续了经典的法国优雅设计。</p><p>当然，这款电动自行车独特的设计也与其技术性能相匹配，42 个电池组确保其能够行驶 100 公里，仅需 2.5 小时即可完成充电。</p><p>每辆自行车都配有无钥匙点火系统，可通过智能手机进行控制。此外，它还配备了一个屏幕，显示包括里程、电池电量和速度在内的基础信息。整款车均是在法国设计、制造完成的，皮革马鞍搭配碳纤维框架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201141M6O0g4naQ3iDb98m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201141iJ23IWcrBRlQE1AC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201141B4caPTxpDoXHm1kN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201142CGWJ5OR3k2XNFlSK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666156\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201141XT9FYx2oZO1ChGdP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668203\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201144iTr3UfzlthnpyWjv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658986\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.coleen-france.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">COLEEN</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Experimental Series of Footwear by Nicole McLaughlin</h3><p>Nicole McLaughlin 本是为 Reebok 的 Cla​​ssics Apparel 做平面设计，但她的 Instagram 却写着：「making highly entertaining footwear out of scraps.」究竟她的鞋子又有多娱乐性？</p><p>她的作品可以是 Ralph Lauren Polo 组成的拖鞋，又可以是羽毛球鞋组成的“钉鞋”，最受欢迎的鞋应该是用 Nikon 相机带整成的 Teva 型凉鞋。</p><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201609dmI5wtOcoLh9qgni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.955000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201221WvZ0a8tsdCrb5qhG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201221b1U7puqKQZVidDMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.957055\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019011020122346B3vL5RO1tis8VY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.958652\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901102012235MLDNUnVqyZ6uTeA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.930982\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190110201224JbS2vIRY8LPUwk67.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.948012\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}